{
  "stem": "802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they also were able to return home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, when the Germans entered-- well, maybe I should mention what I wanted to mention about my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only about eight years ago, something like that, I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember being in the kitchen and thinking of my father, and I felt tremendous anger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was anger and such anguish that I find it difficult to describe, because, for the first time, I came face-to-face with the fact that he left us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a terrible, terrible feeling, and also one that was permeated with guilt, because how could I feel angry at this angel who did so much for us?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'll tell you what he did for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, ultimately, you know, I made peace with this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in some way, it was a kind of catharsis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the anger that I felt as a child that was repressed kind of emerged and sort of spilled over for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not that I was dysfunctional.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I functioned quite well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was teaching, I was doing everything that I had to do, but there was pain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was mostly pain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I spoke with my sister about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she never experienced this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she's an extremely sensitive person and also one who is keenly aware of herself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That is to say, her feelings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She didn't feel this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In some way, she's wiser than I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'm not saying it just to praise her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She really is an extraordinary woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she somehow-- although she's younger than I, and she was younger at the time, she was able to integrate it better than I did.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But anyway, it was a kind of purging for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He left for-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
